(32, 'Female', 'Indonesia', 'University / higher education', 'KETUA PROGRAM STUDI', 'Faculty Member and Teachers', 'Education & Educational Administration', 'Public Health', 7, 7, 6, 6, 6, 7, 6, 7, 'The presenters are engaging and informative, the material given also very interesting and the discussion also packed in good form', 'I think overall this event was well planned', '- I suggest maybe we can be gived more time to recreation, so we can relax while visit famous place where that event held\r\n- More time to sosialize with friends from different regions\r\n- if we can reshedule our ticket to back in our place, please give information before because I know it can when I was in airport\r\n', 6, 6, 6, 7, 7, 6, '" One Health Concept and Knowledge"', 'I work on campus/university as a lecturer and teach health science (human health) certainly be closely related to the one health concept and I think one health concept can be included in the new curriculum for student learning', 'From my friend who took part in GHTL activities last year', 'Hopefully I can be a participant in the next INDOHUN event', 'IN2.1.1'),
(33, 'Male', 'Indonesia', 'Government / public sector', 'Researcher', 'Researcher / Scientist', 'Human Health (Nursing, Public Health, Medicine)', 'Education', 7, 7, 6, 6, 6, 7, 7, 7, '1. Good and Communicative Speakers\r\n2. The Training represents the majority of participansts from 34 Provinces in Indonesia', '1. The training must be well orginize\r\n2. The time for field based learning must be improve and increased\r\n3. The Speakers from Ministry of Health need to be involved ', 'Overall, nice and good event', 5, 6, 5, 7, 7, 5, 'Collabooration and Partnership', 'Because i work in Ministry of Health', 'From my colleagues and Indohun Website', 'None', 'IN2.1.1'),
