(35, 'Female', 'Indonesia', 'Government / public sector', 'Staff', 'Government Official', 'Human Health (Nursing, Public Health, Medicine)', 'Other', 7, 7, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 7, 'Materi yang diberikan padat dan jelas sehingga mudah dimengerti.', 'Pelaksanaan acara diatur semenarik mungkin, dengan setiap peserta dapat mengeksplore kemampuan secara maksimal.', 'Panitia lebih kompak dengan peserta sehingga terjalin bonding yang kuat.', 7, 7, 5, 6, 6, 4, 'Belajar bekerjasama dalam satu kelompok yang berbeda latar belakang pendidikan.', 'Dalam penyusunan program kegiatan, harus mempertimbangkan program yang berdampak nyata bagi peningkatan kualitas kesehatan masyarakat dan melibatkan sektor lain (disiplin ilmu lain) dalam pelaksanaannya.', 'Melalui postingan di group facebook. (Group awardee Kesehatan LPDP)', 'Publikasi kegiatan ini dapat ditingkatkan, khususnya bagi alumni dapat dipublikasikan kegiatan Indohun yang lain sehingga dapat lebih meningkatkan kualitas alumni. ', 'IN2.1.1'),
(36, 'Female', 'Indonesia', 'Government / public sector', 'Staff at Epidemiology Department', 'Government Official', 'Animal Health (Veterinary Medicine, Zoology)', 'Veterinary Medicine', 7, 7, 4, 3, 6, 4, 3, 6, 'multidiscipline, one health, and zoonosis', 'hope the next event well organized than before', '', 6, 7, 7, 6, 6, 6, 'one health for the world', 'i can make a new collaboration from multidiscipline field especially to prevent us from zoonotic disease by ongoing emerging and re-emerging disease surveillance programme', 'From my co-worker and the internet', 'This is a great event and a great moment', 'IN2.1.1'),
(37, 'Male', 'Indonesia', 'Non-Government / non-profit organization', 'Coordinator Project', 'Other', 'Human Health (Nursing, Public Health, Medicine)', 'Nursing', 7, 7, 7, 5, 7, 6, 7, 7, '1. Jaringan\r\n2. Metode pembelajaran\r\n3. Nara sumber yang kompeten di bidangnya', '', '1. dibuthkan perbaikan pengorgaisasian pelatihan yang disesuaikan dengan peserta pelatihan\r\n2. Perlu ditambah waktu bagi peserta untuk membangun ruang diskusi sekaligus melakukan simulasi dari pelatihan yang sudah di dapat', 4, 7, 4, 5, 7, 7, 'Networking ke donor', 'Saya sedang mengembangkan proyek peningkatan akses layanan kesehatan dan layanan pendidikan suku adat marjinal di Provinsi Jambi dan RIau', 'Dari teman', 'Pelatihan ini dapat dibuat terfokus pada daerah yang sudah mempunyai alumni. Para alumni pelatihan ini dapat diorganisir untuk mengembangkan konsep "one health" dalam lingkup wilayah yang terjangkau alumni. Pengawasan dan pembelajaran dari wilayah tersebut dapat menjadi solusi bahkan menjadi bahan tambahan materi pelatihan INDOHUN. ', 'IN2.1.1'),
(39, 'Male', 'Indonesia', 'Government / public sector', 'Researcher', 'Researcher / Scientist', 'Human Health (Nursing, Public Health, Medicine)', 'Education', 6, 6, 6, 4, 6, 6, 5, 6, 'Leadership training and involvement of participants during the training were the most valuable feature of this training. ', 'Detail information on facility limitations (no internet access in room and poor cell phone signal) could be helpful.', 'Overall, the training went well.', 6, 7, 5, 7, 7, 6, 'Leadership and communication skills.', 'This event was related to my work in term of building the network for collaboration.', 'Whastapp Group', 'Combination with Achievement and motivational training would make unforgettable memories.', 'IN2.1.1'),
(40, 'Male', 'Indonesia', 'Government / public sector', 'Head of Puskeswan Koto Baru', 'Government Official', 'Animal Health (Veterinary Medicine, Zoology)', 'Veterinary Medicine', 6, 6, 5, 5, 6, 5, 6, 6, 'Facilitators experiences and training concept', 'Coordination and information between organizer and facilitator to participants must be clear and not confusing', 'I hope this even have regulary time especially to profesional in order to accelerate one health application at field. \r\nTo the organizer team must be increase their communication skill with the participant,sometime their communication and acts is not represent as a leader that We learn together and hope the Organizer team more easy to talk with participant\r\nOverall this even have good impact for Our mindset and work in the future', 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 'Leadership and Communication was the importants lesson that I learned at this even.', 'As a Leader at Puskeswan. I should have good leadership and communication in order to increase Our services to the community and collaboration with other profesional / transdicipline to prevent and overcome the outbreak especially zoonotic diseases', 'From My friend in Whats app message', 'I hope We have alumnus gathering in order sharing the experiences post training and I hope Indohun will alway increase their alumnus knowledge', 'IN2.1.1'),
