(46, 'Female', 'Indonesia', 'University / higher education', 'Lecturer', 'Faculty Member and Teachers', 'Human Health (Nursing, Public Health, Medicine)', 'Public Health', 7, 7, 6, 6, 7, 5, 6, 6, 'The committee was always ready to serve and help, and also the trainers were fun and informative.', '1. Communication between the committee should be improved, so there is no difference in information.\r\n2. The giving of the exercise to the participants should be clear, especially if it is written.', '', 7, 5, 6, 7, 7, 7, 'Teamwork (collaboration) and communication.', 'This event is relevant to my job as a lecturer which is doing tridharma duty i.e. the application of discipline and giving information about one health to the students (education), health promotion especially one health to the public (field work) and research related to one health (zoonotic and nutrition) because my expertise in field of nutrition.', 'Social media (instagram).', '', 'IN2.1.1'),
